  <steps>
    <step num="0">Combine pasta, water, and 1 pinch of salt in a microwave-safe mug and stir to combine. </step>
    <step num="1">Microwave on high for 4-5 minutes, or until ninety percent of water has been absorbed. </step>
    <step num="2">Add almond milk, vegan butter, nutritional yeast, and 1 pinch of salt, and stir well until combined. </step>
    <step num="3">Microwave for 30 more seconds. </step>
    <step num="4">Stir again and sprinkle on paprika to taste. </step>
    <step num="5">Enjoy! </step>
  </steps>
